{"tid":2508992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"由幾時開始你哋見到另一半會覺得有壓力","createTime":"2021-04-29T06:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:34:30.000Z","uid":117822,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01efece6a7718e58e858187b2d605ddb0946c58d","tid":2508992,"uid":117822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"我另一半好容易發脾氣，仲會玩消失，當我搵佢佢就會話我好雷。我同佢講多兩句佢又話我鬧佢<br />\n到依加我覺得我愈黎愈怕佢 好想搵佢又好怕佢發脾氣<br />\n但明明早幾日見完無咩野咁 <br />\n<br />\n有無情侶分開同見面係兩個人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友安慰左我好多次 但我都係唔識點處理<br />\n已經心累了 但我想再嘗試努力下 希望有少少改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1999 依加好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d702de37f0926658616cdfbc9737579d720f2ef","tid":2508992,"uid":252972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:55:00.000Z","msg":"好雷..."},{"pid":"63ab82b7b3a60971ed1a68cb40f63095f1a85e0c","tid":2508992,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair準備分手 開心～"},{"pid":"0c8ba914c44b87737ba7246ed28a9c1011e7fe19","tid":2508992,"uid":117822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d702de37f0926658616cdfbc9737579d720f2ef","tid":2508992,"uid":252972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:55:00.000Z","msg":"好雷..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"佢嘅形容詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0182fd0aab7de0a7fb9fcc4a26fc78ba14a886","tid":2508992,"uid":188411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"掠完邪骨另一半打電話俾自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n